						<summary>

						<p>Slab setup near the house of the Patel.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Rāmachandra 1292 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This very much damaged record mentions the rule of Yādava Rāmachandra. Here only the date and the village Bāguḷahāḻu can be made out. It seems to record the death of a hero.</p>						

						<p>It is dated in the cyclic year Nandana, Āsvija, ba. 13, Monday. It corresponds to 1292 A.D., October 9, Thursday [The Śaka year was 1214].</p>						

						</summary>
